WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

2
00:06:59.710 --> 00:07:03.506
Hello. hello. Please show your tickets.

3
00:07:05.675 --> 00:07:08.136
- Eunice?! From the music video?
- That's me!

4
00:07:16.477 --> 00:07:18.229
I'm your number one "Eunit."

5
00:07:18.312 --> 00:07:19.522
Really? Thank you!

6
00:07:19.605 --> 00:07:22.733
I can get you and your friends
through the VIP entrance.

7
00:07:22.817 --> 00:07:24.068
Really?

8
00:07:26.654 --> 00:07:29.866
Thank you! Find me later
and let's take a picture together!

9
00:07:29.949 --> 00:07:31.159
Thank you!

10
00:11:16.676 --> 00:11:18.761
You said it wasn't scary!

11
00:17:13.407 --> 00:17:14.241
Sorry.

12
00:20:12.377 --> 00:20:13.837
I'm sorry.

13
00:21:26.368 --> 00:21:28.745
Don't take my picture!
I said stop!

14
00:22:47.699 --> 00:22:49.826
Checking your grades again?

15
00:22:49.910 --> 00:22:53.872
Why were you so worried?
You've never gotten less than an A.

16
00:22:53.955 --> 00:22:55.832
If I get even one bad grade.

17
00:22:55.916 --> 00:22:58.043
there’s a chance that I won’t get
into Seoul National University.

18
00:22:58.126 --> 00:23:00.629
I know that's the path
you have always talked about.

19
00:23:00.712 --> 00:23:02.589
but you have more options now.

20
00:23:03.131 --> 00:23:07.469
I used to think I'd always be a VIP.

21
00:23:07.552 --> 00:23:10.639
Honestly. today while we were out.

22
00:23:11.264 --> 00:23:13.558
you showed me
there's more than one way to live.

23
00:23:14.851 --> 00:23:17.229
Both of our lives are different now.

24
00:25:21.645 --> 00:25:22.812
So. what's wrong?

25
00:25:38.495 --> 00:25:39.913
Min Ho…

26
00:25:42.832 --> 00:25:44.000
I…

27
00:25:47.045 --> 00:25:48.713
I think I'm pregnant.

28
00:25:55.512 --> 00:25:56.513
Paris…

29
00:25:59.015 --> 00:26:00.058
that night.

